layout.house_prompt: A community center with a main hall, four activity rooms, a kitchen, an office, a reception, a locker room, a hallway, two bathrooms, and a storage room. The main hall has a stage and rows of chairs. The first activity room has tables and chairs for crafts. The second activity room has yoga mats and a mirror on the wall. The third activity room has a ping pong table. The fourth activity room has easels and stools for art class. The kitchen has a refrigerator, a stove, and a counter. The office has a desk with a chair and a computer. The reception has a desk with a computer. The locker room has lockers and a bench. The hallway has a bulletin board on the wall. The first bathroom has a toilet and a sink. The second bathroom has a toilet and a sink. The storage room has shelves with boxes.

hallway.text_description: A modern, functional community-center hallway with durable finishes and a bulletin board mounted on the wall.

kitchen.text_description: A modern, functional community-center kitchen with a refrigerator, a stove, and a counter.

main_hall.text_description: A modern, functional community-center main hall with a dedicated raised stage platform in a shallow stage alcove/proscenium zone along one short end, and rows of chairs facing the stage.

activity_room_yoga.text_description: A modern, functional activity room for yoga with yoga mats and a mirror on the wall.

activity_room_art.text_description: A modern, functional activity room for art class with easels and stools for art class.
